WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 5=

00:02:01.620 --> 00:02:02.570 line:80%
It's been three days.

00:02:04.460 --> 00:02:05.590 line:80%
You haven't figured it out?

00:02:31.740 --> 00:02:32.580 line:80%
Yuanfeng.

00:02:34.140 --> 00:02:35.560 line:80%
Did you go to Chang Fort that night?

00:02:36.290 --> 00:02:37.490 line:80%
Chang Ning, don't do this.

00:02:38.990 --> 00:02:39.880 line:80%
Mr. Chang,

00:02:40.190 --> 00:02:41.250 line:80%
look at Yuanfeng now.

00:02:41.250 --> 00:02:42.580 line:80%
Why push him?

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:43.560 line:80%
Tell me.

00:02:58.830 --> 00:02:59.670 line:80%
Yuanfeng...

00:03:00.650 --> 00:03:01.490 line:80%
Yuanfeng...

00:03:05.710 --> 00:03:06.570 line:80%
Where's Ms. Luo?

00:03:08.340 --> 00:03:09.180 line:80%
Yes.

00:03:24.740 --> 00:03:25.580 line:80%
Yuanying,

00:03:26.690 --> 00:03:28.090 line:80%
you've been avenged.

00:03:29.190 --> 00:03:30.650 line:80%
You can rest easy.

00:03:38.630 --> 00:03:40.360 line:80%
♪In days gone by♪

00:03:40.670 --> 00:03:42.220 line:80%
♪Willows swayed gently♪

00:03:42.520 --> 00:03:45.270 line:80%
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

00:03:46.240 --> 00:03:47.430 line:80%
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:48.910 line:80%
♪A fleeting glance♪

00:03:49.080 --> 00:03:49.990 line:80%
♪And then♪

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.950 line:80%
♪Love consumed me♪

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:55.310 line:80%
♪Now I think of you♪

00:03:55.710 --> 00:03:57.350 line:80%
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

00:03:57.610 --> 00:03:58.950 line:80%
♪Alas, we parted♪

00:03:58.960 --> 00:04:01.150 line:80%
♪Longing for your return♪

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.230 line:80%
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:03.710 line:80%
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

00:04:03.720 --> 00:04:04.750 line:80%
♪Scattered petals♪

00:04:04.760 --> 00:04:06.990 line:80%
♪Cover the ground♪

00:04:07.180 --> 00:04:08.020 line:80%
Yuanying.

00:04:08.050 --> 00:04:10.310 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:04:10.490 --> 00:04:12.520 line:80%
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

00:04:12.540 --> 00:04:13.650 line:80%
Let's go home.

00:04:15.190 --> 00:04:17.910 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:04:18.010 --> 00:04:22.000 line:80%
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

00:04:22.660 --> 00:04:25.360 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:04:25.540 --> 00:04:29.890 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:04:30.050 --> 00:04:32.770 line:80%
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

00:04:33.010 --> 00:04:38.890 line:80%
♪Tears are like pearls♪

00:04:41.260 --> 00:04:43.480 line:80%
♪Such should be♪

00:04:47.330 --> 00:04:48.980 line:80%
Ms. Luo went to Chang Fort,

00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:51.870 line:80%
so you recognized her early.

00:04:55.470 --> 00:04:56.520 line:80%
Why didn't you tell me?

00:04:59.660 --> 00:05:00.620 line:80%
Why did you protect her?

00:05:01.220 --> 00:05:02.060 line:80%
What do you want?

00:05:03.420 --> 00:05:05.213 line:80%
She wants to expose
Qiu Yuanfeng's true face.

00:05:06.140 --> 00:05:07.100 line:80%
I must help her.

00:05:12.140 --> 00:05:13.700 line:80%
Ms. Luo shouldn't have ended like that.

00:05:14.140 --> 00:05:14.980 line:80%
If I could...

00:05:14.980 --> 00:05:16.460 line:80%
She used Thunderstorm so close to him.

00:05:17.700 --> 00:05:18.660 line:80%
She was ready

00:05:18.660 --> 00:05:20.380 line:80%
to die with Qiu Yuanfeng.

00:05:20.866 --> 00:05:21.979 line:80%
No one could've stopped her.

00:05:23.100 --> 00:05:24.820 line:80%
We will remember the story

00:05:25.860 --> 00:05:26.780 line:80%
of Ms. Luo and Mr. Wu.

00:05:29.100 --> 00:05:30.140 line:80%
So will the world.

00:05:30.500 --> 00:05:31.460 line:80%
But what use is that?

00:05:32.980 --> 00:05:34.260 line:80%
In the end, it's all in vain.

00:05:39.420 --> 00:05:40.420 line:80%
Mr. Wu,

00:05:42.140 --> 00:05:43.020 line:80%
my aunt,

00:05:44.340 --> 00:05:45.420 line:80%
and Uncle Chang.

00:05:46.820 --> 00:05:48.580 line:80%
They shed blood for Jianghu.

00:05:49.340 --> 00:05:50.180 line:80%
And the result?

00:05:52.980 --> 00:05:54.246 line:80%
I never wanted to enter Jianghu,

00:05:55.980 --> 00:05:57.420 line:80%
but as soon as I stepped outside,

00:06:00.540 --> 00:06:01.540 line:80%
it was Jianghu.

00:06:03.380 --> 00:06:05.140 line:80%
Fate is cruel, treating all as equals.

00:06:07.100 --> 00:06:07.940 line:80%
You can choose

00:06:08.380 --> 00:06:09.220 line:80%
to change your fate

00:06:10.140 --> 00:06:11.260 line:80%
or do nothing.

00:06:13.420 --> 00:06:14.460 line:80%
You can choose to avenge

00:06:15.740 --> 00:06:17.180 line:80%
and vent grievances.

00:06:19.700 --> 00:06:20.940 line:80%
This was their choice.

00:07:01.860 --> 00:07:02.700 line:80%
Lei Xiuming,

00:07:03.733 --> 00:07:05.593 line:80%
I can understand your absence
at the memorial,

00:07:06.500 --> 00:07:08.740 line:80%
but today, you didn't attend Yuanrong

00:07:09.100 --> 00:07:09.940 line:80%
and Wu's funeral?

00:07:11.140 --> 00:07:12.500 line:80%
Death is like a snuffed lamp.

00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:14.560 line:80%
What's the point of going?

00:07:15.700 --> 00:07:17.420 line:80%
Besides, it's a cenotaph.

00:07:17.660 --> 00:07:18.740 line:80%
So what?

00:07:19.420 --> 00:07:20.260 line:80%
Lei Xiuming,

00:07:20.340 --> 00:07:21.500 line:80%
you're still alive.

00:07:21.940 --> 00:07:23.180 line:80%
Have you forgotten the time

00:07:23.180 --> 00:07:24.420 line:80%
we drank from the same bowl?

00:07:24.900 --> 00:07:26.140 line:80%
Breeze.

00:07:38.260 --> 00:07:39.100 line:80%
Let's drink Breeze

00:07:39.260 --> 00:07:40.380 line:80%
and enjoy ourselves.

00:07:40.940 --> 00:07:42.340 line:80%
Enjoy!

00:07:43.220 --> 00:07:44.500 line:80%
Come on, cheers!

00:07:46.980 --> 00:07:47.860 line:80%
Come on, drink!

00:07:47.860 --> 00:07:48.710 line:80%
Come on.

00:07:48.710 --> 00:07:49.870 line:80%
Zhao said Yuanrong

00:07:51.580 --> 00:07:53.820 line:80%
went to the wine cellar
before the memorial

00:07:56.540 --> 00:07:58.100 line:80%
to find Breeze.

00:08:08.980 --> 00:08:10.260 line:80%
Good!

00:08:11.340 --> 00:08:12.180 line:80%
I haven't forgotten.

00:08:14.340 --> 00:08:15.740 line:80%
But my martial arts are ruined.

00:08:17.500 --> 00:08:18.700 line:80%
Other than catching my breath,

00:08:18.700 --> 00:08:19.740 line:80%
what else can I do?

00:08:21.100 --> 00:08:22.060 line:80%
Among us,

00:08:23.020 --> 00:08:24.460 line:80%
some are dead,

00:08:26.460 --> 00:08:27.300 line:80%
and some are maimed.

00:08:29.380 --> 00:08:30.340 line:80%
Yet who caused all this?

00:08:30.340 --> 00:08:32.100 line:80%
Was it Nie Hengcheng? Or...

00:08:38.540 --> 00:08:40.060 line:80%
Now, they are all dead.

00:08:41.460 --> 00:08:42.300 line:80%
Tell me.

00:08:43.500 --> 00:08:44.540 line:80%
Who can I blame?

00:08:48.260 --> 00:08:49.580 line:80%
Who can I hate?

00:08:54.260 --> 00:08:55.100 line:80%
Xiuming,

00:08:55.660 --> 00:08:56.500 line:80%
tomorrow,

00:08:56.740 --> 00:08:57.700 line:80%
Xiaofeng and I

00:08:58.860 --> 00:09:00.260 line:80%
will leave Qingque Sect.

00:09:18.460 --> 00:09:19.300 line:80%
Tomorrow,

00:09:19.940 --> 00:09:21.300 line:80%
I'll leave with Lord Cai.

00:09:22.580 --> 00:09:23.420 line:80%
After this,

00:09:23.780 --> 00:09:25.260 line:80%
let's forget each other.

00:09:26.420 --> 00:09:27.580 line:80%
We won't meet again.

00:09:28.300 --> 00:09:29.820 line:80%
We have treasures across the lands.

00:09:30.660 --> 00:09:32.140 line:80%
- You...
- Donate them, please.

00:09:32.827 --> 00:09:34.407 line:80%
I've loved literature, not martial arts.

00:09:34.660 --> 00:09:37.500 line:80%
This life, being a teacher is enough.

00:09:38.660 --> 00:09:39.500 line:80%
Even with a fortune,

00:09:39.500 --> 00:09:40.580 line:80%
I'm still powerless.

00:09:40.759 --> 00:09:42.739 line:80%
Perhaps it's a misfortune
rather than a blessing.

00:09:43.340 --> 00:09:44.380 line:80%
An innocent man bears guilt

00:09:44.700 --> 00:09:45.960 line:80%
because of the jewel he carries.

00:09:46.940 --> 00:09:47.780 line:80%
Fine.

00:09:48.060 --> 00:09:49.140 line:80%
Then, as he hoped,

00:09:50.260 --> 00:09:51.180 line:80%
be an ordinary person.

00:09:51.820 --> 00:09:52.660 line:80%
I heard

00:09:53.620 --> 00:09:54.833 line:80%
that before Qiu Yuanfeng died,

00:09:55.700 --> 00:09:56.540 line:80%
you asked him.

00:09:57.300 --> 00:09:58.140 line:80%
Was it him?

00:09:58.540 --> 00:09:59.940 line:80%
The culprit may be someone else.

00:10:01.540 --> 00:10:02.980 line:80%
I'll find him

00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:06.220 line:80%
and cut him into pieces.

00:10:14.900 --> 00:10:16.060 line:80%
Your parents are gone.

00:10:16.300 --> 00:10:17.740 line:80%
I should've stayed for a few days,

00:10:18.340 --> 00:10:19.740 line:80%
but my wife is ill.

00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:21.100 line:80%
I must return to care for her.

00:10:21.820 --> 00:10:22.660 line:80%
Zhao,

00:10:23.300 --> 00:10:24.980 line:80%
Jianghu erupts again.

00:10:25.580 --> 00:10:27.620 line:80%
With the successive tragedies.

00:10:28.740 --> 00:10:30.100 line:80%
You and Yuqi's marriage

00:10:31.020 --> 00:10:32.140 line:80%
should be arranged.

00:10:39.940 --> 00:10:40.780 line:80%
Uncle Zhou,

00:10:41.660 --> 00:10:44.060 line:80%
I still haven't figured everything out.

00:10:45.100 --> 00:10:47.140 line:80%
I know you still think about Ms. Luo,

00:10:47.860 --> 00:10:49.540 line:80%
but years of battle have caused

00:10:49.540 --> 00:10:50.740 line:80%
countless deaths and injuries.

00:10:50.940 --> 00:10:53.380 line:80%
Many things can't be judged
by normal logic.

00:10:53.660 --> 00:10:54.660 line:80%
However deep you probe,

00:10:55.100 --> 00:10:57.300 line:80%
those who left will not return.

00:10:58.020 --> 00:10:59.420 line:80%
The sooner you marry Yuqi,

00:10:59.740 --> 00:11:00.866 line:80%
the sooner your parents and I

00:11:01.060 --> 00:11:02.220 line:80%
can rest easy.

00:11:04.580 --> 00:11:05.620 line:80%
If Aunt were here,

00:11:08.140 --> 00:11:09.580 line:80%
would she just stand by?

00:11:21.300 --> 00:11:22.140 line:80%
She wouldn't,

00:11:23.340 --> 00:11:24.180 line:80%
but she'd hope

00:11:24.660 --> 00:11:25.860 line:80%
you would.

00:11:27.300 --> 00:11:29.100 line:80%
She arranged your betrothal with Yuqi

00:11:29.940 --> 00:11:30.860 line:80%
to keep you

00:11:31.420 --> 00:11:33.420 line:80%
from Jianghu disputes.

00:11:43.740 --> 00:11:44.580 line:80%
Master.

00:11:46.820 --> 00:11:47.660 line:80%
Zhao,

00:11:48.820 --> 00:11:50.700 line:80%
after finishing the memorial,

00:11:50.780 --> 00:11:51.820 line:80%
I came

00:11:51.820 --> 00:11:52.660 line:80%
to see you

00:11:52.660 --> 00:11:53.500 line:80%
and Ning.

00:11:55.060 --> 00:11:55.900 line:80%
Where is Zhou?

00:11:56.100 --> 00:11:56.940 line:80%
He just left.

00:11:56.951 --> 00:11:58.233 line:80%
He always wants to trick you

00:11:58.244 --> 00:12:00.100 line:80%
into going to Peiqiong Manor.

00:12:00.580 --> 00:12:01.420 line:80%
I really feared

00:12:02.020 --> 00:12:03.220 line:80%
you might go with him.

00:12:03.780 --> 00:12:05.100 line:80%
Master, rest assured.

00:12:05.460 --> 00:12:06.300 line:80%
Now that I'm here,

00:12:06.700 --> 00:12:07.860 line:80%
I'll stay for a whole year.

00:12:08.780 --> 00:12:10.820 line:80%
Keep your word.

00:12:13.580 --> 00:12:14.420 line:80%
Ning,

00:12:15.580 --> 00:12:16.740 line:80%
I didn't expect you

00:12:17.340 --> 00:12:19.700 line:80%
to recognize Thunderstorm at a glance.

00:12:22.100 --> 00:12:23.700 line:80%
Watch out! It's Thunderstorm!

00:12:29.820 --> 00:12:31.180 line:80%
My father told me.

00:12:32.460 --> 00:12:33.500 line:80%
So did my aunt.

00:12:35.100 --> 00:12:37.020 line:80%
I never expected
a random demon sect weapon

00:12:37.020 --> 00:12:37.860 line:80%
to be so deadly.

00:12:38.060 --> 00:12:39.180 line:80%
The demon sect is brutal.

00:12:39.860 --> 00:12:41.140 line:80%
You've never experienced it.

00:12:42.140 --> 00:12:42.980 line:80%
I hope

00:12:43.940 --> 00:12:45.580 line:80%
you never will.

00:12:51.620 --> 00:12:52.740 line:80%
That's also Aunt's wish.

00:12:55.220 --> 00:12:56.060 line:80%
Rest early.

00:12:56.460 --> 00:12:57.300 line:80%
I'll take my leave.

00:13:22.060 --> 00:13:22.900 line:80%
Zhao.

00:13:23.460 --> 00:13:25.300 line:80%
Why are you practicing alone today?

00:13:25.580 --> 00:13:26.860 line:80%
After the memorial,

00:13:26.940 --> 00:13:28.830 line:80%
everyone was deeply shaken,

00:13:29.060 --> 00:13:30.320 line:80%
both angry and confused.

00:13:30.740 --> 00:13:32.330 line:80%
They felt unable to focus,

00:13:32.460 --> 00:13:33.770 line:80%
unsure of the path ahead.

00:13:33.900 --> 00:13:36.300 line:80%
So, Yuzhi let them return
to calm themselves.

00:13:36.700 --> 00:13:38.380 line:80%
Then why do you keep practicing?

00:13:38.380 --> 00:13:40.380 line:80%
Martial arts exist to uphold justice.

00:13:41.100 --> 00:13:42.620 line:80%
Whether others act wrongly or not,

00:13:42.860 --> 00:13:44.740 line:80%
upholding justice itself is not wrong.

00:13:45.340 --> 00:13:46.260 line:80%
As long as it is right,

00:13:46.620 --> 00:13:47.740 line:80%
I won't regret it.

00:13:49.780 --> 00:13:50.620 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:51.540 --> 00:13:53.020 line:80%
Aunt also said this.

00:13:54.140 --> 00:13:56.580 line:80%
There's nothing in life to regret.

00:13:57.340 --> 00:13:58.460 line:80%
If you think it's right,

00:13:58.980 --> 00:13:59.820 line:80%
do it.

00:14:01.580 --> 00:14:02.420 line:80%
Zhao!

00:14:04.700 --> 00:14:05.700 line:80%
What do you need?

00:14:06.220 --> 00:14:08.380 line:80%
I just went to do acupuncture for Chang.

00:14:08.380 --> 00:14:09.340 line:80%
Why isn't he there?

00:14:14.900 --> 00:14:16.020 line:80%
Master already suspects you.

00:14:17.620 --> 00:14:19.100 line:80%
You can't continue to stay.

00:14:24.460 --> 00:14:25.380 line:80%
Let's part here.

00:14:30.020 --> 00:14:30.860 line:80%
Okay.

00:15:58.500 --> 00:15:59.406 line:80%
All have taken poison.

00:16:00.700 --> 00:16:01.820 line:80%
The Demonic Camp.

00:16:03.300 --> 00:16:04.500 line:80%
You didn't kill them?

00:16:04.886 --> 00:16:06.766 line:80%
An insider killed
the cliff-guarding disciples,

00:16:06.940 --> 00:16:08.180 line:80%
leading the Demonic Camp here.

00:16:08.460 --> 00:16:09.620 line:80%
Before the swords were drawn,

00:16:09.740 --> 00:16:11.340 line:80%
they were ambushed and killed,

00:16:11.820 --> 00:16:12.820 line:80%
completely unprepared.

00:16:13.500 --> 00:16:15.180 line:80%
To kill 8 disciples simultaneously,

00:16:16.100 --> 00:16:17.520 line:80%
there must be more than one insider.

00:16:19.940 --> 00:16:21.220 line:80%
The sword marks are curved.

00:16:23.260 --> 00:16:24.246 line:80%
Aunt said the 13th move

00:16:24.580 --> 00:16:26.260 line:80%
of the Taichu Swordsmanship

00:16:26.740 --> 00:16:28.140 line:80%
requires a lower body,

00:16:28.420 --> 00:16:29.340 line:80%
an upward thrust,

00:16:29.860 --> 00:16:30.940 line:80%
and hilt rotation

00:16:31.860 --> 00:16:33.140 line:80%
after piercing into one's body.

00:16:38.070 --> 00:16:38.940 line:80%
Oh, no.

00:16:38.980 --> 00:16:40.500 line:80%
Wu Gang and Wu Xiong of Taichu Temple

00:16:40.511 --> 00:16:41.460 line:80%
are recuperating here.

00:16:46.660 --> 00:16:47.500 line:80%
And you left?

00:16:51.860 --> 00:16:52.700 line:80%
Forget it.

00:16:54.060 --> 00:16:54.900 line:80%
Let it be.

00:17:16.740 --> 00:17:17.926 line:80%
These volumes of mindful ways

00:17:18.780 --> 00:17:20.940 line:80%
were gifts from your brother long ago.

00:17:25.340 --> 00:17:27.340 line:80%
Alas, the times have changed.

00:17:31.780 --> 00:17:32.620 line:80%
Master, be careful!

00:17:40.860 --> 00:17:42.300 line:80%
Master!

00:17:48.740 --> 00:17:49.660 line:80%
Master,

00:17:50.253 --> 00:17:51.220 line:80%
this dagger is poisoned.

00:17:51.340 --> 00:17:52.180 line:80%
I guessed it,

00:17:53.100 --> 00:17:54.700 line:80%
so I sealed the acupoints beforehand.

00:17:55.140 --> 00:17:57.226 line:80%
Later, I'll force out the poison,
and I'll be fine.

00:18:00.100 --> 00:18:01.780 line:80%
Master, this is Wu Xiong.

00:18:02.060 --> 00:18:02.900 line:80%
Where is Wu Gang?

00:18:04.940 --> 00:18:07.260 line:80%
Wu Gang went to pay respects to Mr. Wu.

00:18:08.780 --> 00:18:09.860 line:80%
I let Yuzhi go with him.

00:18:11.300 --> 00:18:12.140 line:80%
Oh, no.

00:18:12.700 --> 00:18:13.740 line:80%
Yuzhi is in danger.

00:18:14.020 --> 00:18:15.460 line:80%
Master, heal first.

00:18:15.500 --> 00:18:16.340 line:80%
I'll go save him.

00:18:44.940 --> 00:18:46.620 line:80%
We've treated you both well.

00:18:47.540 --> 00:18:49.380 line:80%
Why collude with the demon sect

00:18:49.620 --> 00:18:50.900 line:80%
to commit such vile acts?

00:18:51.420 --> 00:18:52.373 line:80%
Stop talking nonsense.

00:18:53.260 --> 00:18:55.500 line:80%
If it weren't
for your grandfather's selfishness,

00:18:55.860 --> 00:18:57.980 line:80%
refusing to use Elder Kaiyang
to save my brother,

00:18:58.740 --> 00:19:00.500 line:80%
he wouldn't have ended up

00:19:00.500 --> 00:19:02.060 line:80%
like that.

00:19:03.540 --> 00:19:05.300 line:80%
What a so-called greatest sect.

00:19:06.380 --> 00:19:08.380 line:80%
What a hypocrite.

00:19:08.820 --> 00:19:10.580 line:80%
I did nothing to Mr. Wu.

00:19:11.020 --> 00:19:12.340 line:80%
Why do this to me?

00:19:13.060 --> 00:19:15.100 line:80%
Because you are Yin's grandson.

00:19:15.700 --> 00:19:16.620 line:80%
You deserve death too.

00:19:18.780 --> 00:19:20.260 line:80%
You've been hit by my Nether Aura.

00:19:21.140 --> 00:19:22.140 line:80%
Even if you don't die,

00:19:22.500 --> 00:19:23.700 line:80%
you'll be invalid.

00:19:24.220 --> 00:19:25.060 line:80%
Attack!

00:19:39.220 --> 00:19:40.060 line:80%
Xiong's blade!

00:19:40.740 --> 00:19:41.660 line:80%
Qi Yunke is not dead!

00:19:42.260 --> 00:19:43.100 line:80%
My master is fine!

00:19:44.140 --> 00:19:44.980 line:80%
Zhao, go now.

00:19:45.060 --> 00:19:45.900 line:80%
Don't worry about me.

00:19:46.340 --> 00:19:47.180 line:80%
As long as I live,

00:19:47.900 --> 00:19:48.740 line:80%
I won't let you die.

00:19:58.140 --> 00:19:59.060 line:80%
Sunshine Blade.

00:20:04.940 --> 00:20:06.100 line:80%
My Sunshine Blade

00:20:06.700 --> 00:20:09.100 line:80%
once killed Nie Hengcheng, your chief.

00:20:09.380 --> 00:20:10.500 line:80%
If you want to test it,

00:20:12.140 --> 00:20:12.980 line:80%
come!

00:20:15.860 --> 00:20:16.700 line:80%
Attack!

00:21:13.900 --> 00:21:14.740 line:80%
Zhao!

00:21:40.940 --> 00:21:41.780 line:80%
You didn't leave.

00:21:45.820 --> 00:21:46.700 line:80%
My Smiley is spilled.

00:21:48.460 --> 00:21:49.300 line:80%
You owe me a pack.

00:21:51.260 --> 00:21:53.500 line:80%
Why protect Yin Dai's grandson?

00:21:54.180 --> 00:21:55.460 line:80%
If not for Yin Dai,

00:21:55.940 --> 00:21:57.900 line:80%
Cai Pingshu wouldn't have died.

00:21:59.180 --> 00:22:00.020 line:80%
What did you say?

00:22:01.300 --> 00:22:02.140 line:80%
Back then,

00:22:02.740 --> 00:22:05.620 line:80%
he deliberately...

00:22:10.060 --> 00:22:10.900 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:22:11.900 --> 00:22:12.740 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:22:13.180 --> 00:22:14.020 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:22:14.100 --> 00:22:14.940 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:22:15.420 --> 00:22:16.260 line:80%
Finish it.

00:22:27.420 --> 00:22:28.260 line:80%
Wait a moment.

00:22:28.300 --> 00:22:29.140 line:80%
Alright.

00:22:29.180 --> 00:22:30.020 line:80%
How is it?

00:22:30.900 --> 00:22:32.420 line:80%
- How are you?
- I'm fine.

00:22:32.460 --> 00:22:33.860 line:80%
Here, drink the medicine.

00:22:35.580 --> 00:22:36.420 line:80%
Endure it.

00:22:42.320 --> 00:22:43.546 line:80%
Cold poison entered the veins;

00:22:43.557 --> 00:22:44.803 line:80%
his internal energy was damaged.

00:22:46.180 --> 00:22:47.740 line:80%
Yuzhi is afflicted by Nether Aura.

00:22:49.740 --> 00:22:50.620 line:80%
I never expected

00:22:51.220 --> 00:22:52.060 line:80%
Wu Gang to have

00:22:52.740 --> 00:22:54.380 line:80%
such a sinister martial skill.

00:22:55.540 --> 00:22:56.380 line:80%
Xiuming,

00:22:57.260 --> 00:22:58.180 line:80%
how confident are you?

00:22:59.420 --> 00:23:01.660 line:80%
Wenxun is suppressing his cold poison.

00:23:02.540 --> 00:23:03.380 line:80%
However,

00:23:03.940 --> 00:23:05.140 line:80%
even if controlled,

00:23:05.420 --> 00:23:07.740 line:80%
Yuzhi's power is left at less than 30%.

00:23:10.500 --> 00:23:12.420 line:80%
Father, save Yuzhi!

00:23:12.420 --> 00:23:13.820 line:80%
He must not die!

00:23:13.820 --> 00:23:14.900 line:80%
Stop yelling!

00:23:15.020 --> 00:23:17.260 line:80%
If you keep yelling, Yuzhi will be gone.

00:23:23.580 --> 00:23:24.420 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:23:25.280 --> 00:23:26.240 line:80%
tell all sects

00:23:26.420 --> 00:23:27.380 line:80%
to be vigilant,

00:23:27.660 --> 00:23:29.020 line:80%
lest the demon sect ambush them.

00:23:29.860 --> 00:23:30.700 line:80%
Yes.

00:23:43.740 --> 00:23:46.940 line:80%
He deliberately...

00:23:56.700 --> 00:23:57.540 line:80%
Pingchun!

00:23:58.180 --> 00:23:59.020 line:80%
Pingchun!

00:23:59.580 --> 00:24:00.940 line:80%
Come and save her!

00:24:01.180 --> 00:24:02.020 line:80%
Come!

00:24:02.660 --> 00:24:03.500 line:80%
Hurry!

00:24:06.220 --> 00:24:08.300 line:80%
Those cold-blooded hypocrites

00:24:09.460 --> 00:24:10.900 line:80%
just stood by.

00:24:39.980 --> 00:24:41.860 line:80%
You've been overly protected
by your family.

00:24:43.300 --> 00:24:44.340 line:80%
Once outside,

00:24:45.460 --> 00:24:46.380 line:80%
harden your heart.

00:24:47.140 --> 00:24:47.980 line:80%
I know.

00:24:49.220 --> 00:24:50.700 line:80%
Life and death are common.

00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:52.300 line:80%
If someone is killed,

00:24:52.860 --> 00:24:53.820 line:80%
someone must pay.

00:24:55.300 --> 00:24:56.260 line:80%
Spare a villain,

00:24:57.260 --> 00:24:58.820 line:80%
and more innocents suffer.

00:24:59.580 --> 00:25:01.540 line:80%
Aunt trained me tirelessly
in martial arts,

00:25:02.220 --> 00:25:03.460 line:80%
so I could one day

00:25:04.780 --> 00:25:07.260 line:80%
protect myself and others.

00:25:07.460 --> 00:25:08.340 line:80%
Ms. Cai's plan for you

00:25:09.660 --> 00:25:10.700 line:80%
was also far-reaching.

00:25:11.780 --> 00:25:13.980 line:80%
But I didn't protect Master and Yuzhi.

00:25:15.100 --> 00:25:15.940 line:80%
However strong,

00:25:17.420 --> 00:25:18.660 line:80%
one may still be overwhelmed.

00:25:19.700 --> 00:25:20.660 line:80%
We can only do our best.

00:25:23.060 --> 00:25:23.900 line:80%
Yes.

00:25:25.940 --> 00:25:26.960 line:80%
We can only do our best.

00:25:30.740 --> 00:25:31.700 line:80%
Aren't you leaving?

00:25:31.913 --> 00:25:32.860 line:80%
Why are you still here?

00:25:38.500 --> 00:25:39.940 line:80%
The ones who attacked Qingque Sect

00:25:40.133 --> 00:25:41.460 line:80%
were also from the Demonic Camp.

00:25:41.759 --> 00:25:43.253 line:80%
I want to find them and take revenge.

00:25:46.140 --> 00:25:47.060 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:25:47.460 --> 00:25:49.420 line:80%
feeling guilty toward Ms. Luo,

00:25:49.940 --> 00:25:51.740 line:80%
let those two recover here.

00:25:53.220 --> 00:25:55.300 line:80%
This must also be
part of the demon sect's plan.

00:25:56.180 --> 00:25:57.700 line:80%
A subtle line

00:25:57.900 --> 00:25:59.020 line:80%
runs through.

00:26:00.260 --> 00:26:01.620 line:80%
Ms. Luo came here

00:26:01.740 --> 00:26:03.540 line:80%
but brought these two pawns.

00:26:04.740 --> 00:26:06.300 line:80%
Did Ms. Luo...

00:26:07.220 --> 00:26:08.340 line:80%
She didn't know.

00:26:10.060 --> 00:26:11.460 line:80%
She must've been used.

00:26:18.500 --> 00:26:22.060 line:80%
(A few days later, Chuitian Dock)

00:26:23.980 --> 00:26:24.820 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:26:25.540 --> 00:26:26.760 line:80%
this is Longjiao Incense

00:26:26.940 --> 00:26:27.860 line:80%
for calming the spirit.

00:26:30.300 --> 00:26:31.380 line:80%
And this is

00:26:31.900 --> 00:26:32.940 line:80%
Blood Swallow Congee.

00:26:33.220 --> 00:26:34.500 line:80%
Grandfather left this.

00:26:34.780 --> 00:26:36.060 line:80%
It helps replenish qi.

00:26:40.900 --> 00:26:41.740 line:80%
Yuzhi?

00:26:41.940 --> 00:26:42.780 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:26:45.540 --> 00:26:46.780 line:80%
I want to be alone for a while.

00:26:51.460 --> 00:26:52.460 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:26:53.580 --> 00:26:55.940 line:80%
I know you feel uneasy,

00:26:56.540 --> 00:26:57.460 line:80%
but rest assured.

00:26:57.620 --> 00:26:58.820 line:80%
I heard from Uncle Lei

00:26:59.100 --> 00:27:01.260 line:80%
that once Father uses
Tianhuo Dragon Aura

00:27:01.260 --> 00:27:02.480 line:80%
to channel energy and heal you,

00:27:02.620 --> 00:27:03.633 line:80%
combined with these herbs,

00:27:03.740 --> 00:27:05.660 line:80%
your martial arts will slowly recover.

00:27:11.780 --> 00:27:12.780 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:27:18.380 --> 00:27:19.780 line:80%
you're blaming me.

00:27:20.820 --> 00:27:23.020 line:80%
You think
I shouldn't have killed Wu Gang?

00:27:24.980 --> 00:27:26.220 line:80%
But if I hadn't,

00:27:26.220 --> 00:27:27.340 line:80%
would he have been allowed

00:27:27.340 --> 00:27:28.580 line:80%
to defame Grandfather?

00:27:29.140 --> 00:27:30.020 line:80%
Cai Zhao

00:27:30.180 --> 00:27:31.700 line:80%
always likes to stir up trouble.

00:27:32.006 --> 00:27:33.020 line:80%
If she had heard about it,

00:27:33.020 --> 00:27:34.173 line:80%
she'd have caused more chaos.

00:27:34.460 --> 00:27:35.820 line:80%
Forget the past.

00:27:38.660 --> 00:27:39.500 line:80%
Yes.

00:27:41.180 --> 00:27:42.180 line:80%
Recovery comes first.

00:27:43.780 --> 00:27:44.620 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:27:44.950 --> 00:27:46.983 line:80%
Nanny Mao prepared a herbal bath
in the hot spring,

00:27:47.100 --> 00:27:48.500 line:80%
specially using Grandfather's

00:27:48.500 --> 00:27:50.060 line:80%
Revival Pill.

00:27:50.290 --> 00:27:51.140 line:80%
Let's go.

00:27:51.180 --> 00:27:52.020 line:80%
I'll take you.

00:27:52.540 --> 00:27:53.380 line:80%
No need.

00:27:55.320 --> 00:27:56.660 line:80%
It's been carefully prepared.

00:27:59.060 --> 00:27:59.900 line:80%
Let's go.

00:28:00.220 --> 00:28:01.060 line:80%
No need.

00:28:03.260 --> 00:28:04.100 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:28:04.760 --> 00:28:06.190 line:80%
Lingbo has been sincere with you,

00:28:06.460 --> 00:28:07.606 line:80%
planning all this for you.

00:28:07.617 --> 00:28:08.723 line:80%
And you treat her like this?

00:28:08.940 --> 00:28:09.860 line:80%
Fengchi,

00:28:10.330 --> 00:28:11.540 line:80%
Yuzhi didn't mean it.

00:28:11.860 --> 00:28:12.700 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:28:14.146 --> 00:28:15.452 line:80%
I want to recover in peace alone.

00:28:16.340 --> 00:28:17.300 line:80%
Please go out first.

00:28:20.860 --> 00:28:21.700 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:28:22.580 --> 00:28:23.620 line:80%
I'm your senior brother.

00:28:24.260 --> 00:28:25.500 line:80%
Today, just listen to me

00:28:26.020 --> 00:28:27.100 line:80%
and go with Lingbo to heal.

00:28:30.100 --> 00:28:31.140 line:80%
What's the matter, Fengchi?

00:28:32.500 --> 00:28:33.980 line:80%
Usually, you can't beat Yuzhi,

00:28:34.140 --> 00:28:35.980 line:80%
so today,
taking advantage of his injury,

00:28:36.020 --> 00:28:37.166 line:80%
you show off your power, huh?

00:28:39.213 --> 00:28:39.725 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:28:39.736 --> 00:28:40.900 line:80%
what nonsense are you saying?

00:28:40.900 --> 00:28:42.100 line:80%
Yeah, that's nonsense.

00:28:42.900 --> 00:28:44.180 line:80%
Stop stirring trouble here.

00:28:44.300 --> 00:28:46.180 line:80%
We're just here to check on Yuzhi.

00:28:46.580 --> 00:28:47.420 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:28:48.420 --> 00:28:49.260 line:80%
if nothing else,

00:28:50.660 --> 00:28:52.300 line:80%
you and Fengchi may leave.

00:28:57.180 --> 00:28:58.020 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:29:03.940 --> 00:29:05.286 line:80%
Lately, I've been recovering here,

00:29:05.523 --> 00:29:06.766 line:80%
so I haven't been able to visit.

00:29:07.346 --> 00:29:08.740 line:80%
Thank you both for saving my life.

00:29:10.220 --> 00:29:11.180 line:80%
Your eyes

00:29:11.540 --> 00:29:12.406 line:80%
are better now, right?

00:29:13.220 --> 00:29:14.060 line:80%
Yeah.

00:29:14.660 --> 00:29:15.560 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:29:15.560 --> 00:29:16.620 line:80%
I came to tell you:

00:29:17.260 --> 00:29:18.170 line:80%
My aunt's friend

00:29:18.180 --> 00:29:19.500 line:80%
was once afflicted by Nether Aura

00:29:19.900 --> 00:29:20.780 line:80%
but later recovered.

00:29:21.060 --> 00:29:21.900 line:80%
Really?

00:29:22.020 --> 00:29:22.860 line:80%
Really.

00:29:23.100 --> 00:29:23.940 line:80%
How did it happen?

00:29:24.500 --> 00:29:26.980 line:80%
Apparently, my aunt found
a special herb.

00:29:28.860 --> 00:29:30.380 line:80%
I already sent a letter to my parents.

00:29:30.740 --> 00:29:32.460 line:80%
It should reach them in a few days.

00:29:33.780 --> 00:29:34.620 line:80%
Thank you.

00:29:36.140 --> 00:29:38.700 line:80%
Something's wrong!

00:29:39.140 --> 00:29:40.460 line:80%
After leaving, all sects

00:29:40.460 --> 00:29:41.740 line:80%
were ambushed by the demon sect.

00:29:41.740 --> 00:29:42.580 line:80%
What?

00:29:42.780 --> 00:29:44.820 line:80%
Lord Song went to Yangzhou
to buy a golden tortoise

00:29:44.980 --> 00:29:45.820 line:80%
and avoided it.

00:29:47.860 --> 00:29:49.180 line:80%
Taichu Temple broke apart halfway;

00:29:49.286 --> 00:29:50.835 line:80%
Siqi Sect diverted to marry a concubine.

00:29:50.940 --> 00:29:51.780 line:80%
They also avoided it.

00:29:54.420 --> 00:29:55.369 line:80%
What about my parents?

00:29:55.380 --> 00:29:56.740 line:80%
Mr. Cai's group moved slowly,

00:29:57.140 --> 00:29:58.213 line:80%
so they weren't ambushed.

00:29:59.746 --> 00:30:00.492 line:80%
But Peiqiong Manor

00:30:00.503 --> 00:30:02.026 line:80%
collided directly with the demon sect.

00:30:02.140 --> 00:30:03.180 line:80%
Lord Zhou was injured.

00:30:03.500 --> 00:30:04.340 line:80%
How severe?

00:30:05.460 --> 00:30:07.020 line:80%
Minor scratches.

00:30:07.460 --> 00:30:08.580 line:80%
Yuqi is also fine.

00:30:08.900 --> 00:30:10.140 line:80%
They've returned to the manor.

00:30:11.580 --> 00:30:12.420 line:80%
Fan,

00:30:12.900 --> 00:30:14.500 line:80%
can you speak in one go?

00:30:14.980 --> 00:30:16.020 line:80%
Look at Zhao, so scared.

00:30:19.740 --> 00:30:20.580 line:80%
Right.

00:30:20.700 --> 00:30:21.820 line:80%
Uncle Li said

00:30:21.820 --> 00:30:23.340 line:80%
we must strengthen defenses

00:30:23.500 --> 00:30:24.980 line:80%
and invited many external elites.

00:30:25.420 --> 00:30:26.260 line:80%
Zhao,

00:30:26.300 --> 00:30:27.140 line:80%
you know arrays.

00:30:27.580 --> 00:30:28.900 line:80%
Tomorrow morning, accompany me

00:30:28.973 --> 00:30:30.959 line:80%
to Qingque Town to collect
some array materials.

00:30:32.980 --> 00:30:34.540 line:80%
It seems traveling is getting harder.

00:30:37.100 --> 00:30:37.940 line:80%
Ning,

00:30:38.940 --> 00:30:39.780 line:80%
what's your plan?

00:30:40.580 --> 00:30:41.620 line:80%
I'll go down with you.

00:30:43.459 --> 00:30:44.599 line:80%
There are about to be changes

00:30:45.540 --> 00:30:46.620 line:80%
in Qingque Sect.

00:31:06.180 --> 00:31:07.260 line:80%
If you like it,

00:31:08.060 --> 00:31:09.380 line:80%
maybe there's still a chance...

00:31:09.380 --> 00:31:10.220 line:80%
No need.

00:31:11.860 --> 00:31:12.860 line:80%
After you leave,

00:31:13.100 --> 00:31:14.140 line:80%
go handle your affairs.

00:31:14.699 --> 00:31:15.765 line:80%
Only when free from worries

00:31:15.946 --> 00:31:17.253 line:80%
can you succeed in all endeavors.

00:31:24.220 --> 00:31:25.060 line:80%
Breeze?

00:31:26.020 --> 00:31:27.220 line:80%
I heard from Fan

00:31:27.540 --> 00:31:28.660 line:80%
that before your mother left,

00:31:29.300 --> 00:31:30.786 line:80%
she took the last three jars of Breeze

00:31:30.797 --> 00:31:31.740 line:80%
from the wine cellar.

00:31:32.740 --> 00:31:33.860 line:80%
This is the last jar.

00:31:34.460 --> 00:31:35.580 line:80%
I got it from Uncle Lei.

00:31:36.620 --> 00:31:38.020 line:80%
I promised you before

00:31:38.380 --> 00:31:39.220 line:80%
to protect you

00:31:39.620 --> 00:31:41.020 line:80%
and not let you face

00:31:41.620 --> 00:31:42.460 line:80%
revenge alone.

00:31:43.060 --> 00:31:44.473 line:80%
Now, I fear I'll break that promise.

00:31:46.673 --> 00:31:47.580 line:80%
Please don't blame me.

00:31:53.620 --> 00:31:54.460 line:80%
I won't.

00:32:05.740 --> 00:32:07.340 line:80%
When Mr. Chang died because of me,

00:32:09.740 --> 00:32:11.140 line:80%
I was filled with hatred.

00:32:12.340 --> 00:32:13.420 line:80%
All I wanted was revenge.

00:32:15.900 --> 00:32:16.740 line:80%
But unexpectedly,

00:32:17.460 --> 00:32:18.300 line:80%
in just a few months,

00:32:18.860 --> 00:32:19.700 line:80%
I met you

00:32:20.780 --> 00:32:21.780 line:80%
and experienced things

00:32:22.020 --> 00:32:23.260 line:80%
I never had before.

00:32:23.460 --> 00:32:24.300 line:80%
It's my fortune.

00:32:25.700 --> 00:32:26.540 line:80%
Thank you.

00:32:30.620 --> 00:32:31.460 line:80%
Zhao, rest assured.

00:32:32.820 --> 00:32:34.020 line:80%
I'll avenge the Chang family,

00:32:34.780 --> 00:32:35.620 line:80%
my father,

00:32:36.500 --> 00:32:37.540 line:80%
and myself.

00:32:44.540 --> 00:32:45.400 line:80%
Chang Ning,

00:32:45.410 --> 00:32:46.340 line:80%
no matter who it's for,

00:32:46.660 --> 00:32:47.500 line:80%
you swore

00:32:48.020 --> 00:32:49.380 line:80%
never to use the Disintegration.

00:32:50.020 --> 00:32:50.860 line:80%
Your life

00:32:51.140 --> 00:32:52.126 line:80%
was saved by Uncle Chang,

00:32:52.820 --> 00:32:53.660 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:32:54.340 --> 00:32:55.180 line:80%
Jiang Ning,

00:32:55.380 --> 00:32:56.220 line:80%
and me,

00:32:56.340 --> 00:32:57.780 line:80%
through great effort.

00:32:58.780 --> 00:32:59.620 line:80%
Survive.

00:33:00.700 --> 00:33:01.940 line:80%
Find every way to survive.

00:33:03.380 --> 00:33:04.380 line:80%
If injured,

00:33:04.980 --> 00:33:05.860 line:80%
come back here.

00:33:10.660 --> 00:33:11.580 line:80%
Come to Luoying Valley.

00:33:12.506 --> 00:33:13.613 line:80%
My mother is a great healer.

00:33:13.940 --> 00:33:14.790 line:80%
She's as good

00:33:14.800 --> 00:33:15.680 line:80%
as Uncle Lei.

00:33:17.300 --> 00:33:18.140 line:80%
Sure.

00:33:23.220 --> 00:33:24.820 line:80%
You told me to survive no matter what,

00:33:26.633 --> 00:33:27.786 line:80%
but you should also remember:

00:33:29.580 --> 00:33:30.980 line:80%
No matter when or where,

00:33:32.060 --> 00:33:32.940 line:80%
finish things

00:33:34.180 --> 00:33:35.020 line:80%
when necessary.

00:33:35.900 --> 00:33:36.740 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:33:37.020 --> 00:33:37.940 line:80%
lingering attachments

00:33:39.340 --> 00:33:40.420 line:80%
will lead to ruin.

00:33:49.660 --> 00:33:50.500 line:80%
I'll remember.

00:34:03.660 --> 00:34:06.380 line:80%
(Disciples' Dorm)

00:34:06.380 --> 00:34:07.220 line:80%
Xingjia!

00:34:13.460 --> 00:34:14.300 line:80%
Xingjia?

00:34:15.660 --> 00:34:16.500 line:80%
He's not here.

00:34:19.980 --> 00:34:20.820 line:80%
Zhuang,

00:34:21.980 --> 00:34:22.820 line:80%
where's Xingjia?

00:34:23.026 --> 00:34:24.380 line:80%
I looked for him at the Mao hour,

00:34:24.380 --> 00:34:25.220 line:80%
and he wasn't here.

00:34:25.740 --> 00:34:26.766 line:80%
Did he go to Qingque Town?

00:34:27.380 --> 00:34:29.300 line:80%
(Zhuang Shu)
He said yesterday he'd go there.

00:34:34.820 --> 00:34:35.906 line:80%
Xingjia must be in trouble.

00:34:36.638 --> 00:34:38.212 line:80%
He comes from a wealthy merchant family,

00:34:38.460 --> 00:34:39.300 line:80%
a proper gentleman.

00:34:39.660 --> 00:34:41.460 line:80%
He'd follow the routine
of making the bed,

00:34:42.100 --> 00:34:42.940 line:80%
but look at this bed.

00:34:43.673 --> 00:34:45.039 line:80%
He must've been taken by someone.

00:34:51.340 --> 00:34:52.180 line:80%
Zhao,

00:34:52.540 --> 00:34:53.380 line:80%
have you noticed?

00:34:53.660 --> 00:34:54.620 line:80%
Since just now,

00:34:55.460 --> 00:34:56.740 line:80%
someone has been watching us.

00:35:01.020 --> 00:35:01.860 line:80%
Don't tell anyone

00:35:03.340 --> 00:35:04.180 line:80%
about Fan yet.

00:35:07.340 --> 00:35:08.300 line:80%
Since he's gone,

00:35:09.780 --> 00:35:10.660 line:80%
let's go without him.

00:35:11.500 --> 00:35:12.340 line:80%
Let's go.

00:35:14.940 --> 00:35:16.060 line:80%
After the memorial,

00:35:16.566 --> 00:35:18.439 line:80%
(Qingque Town)
many martial artists came here.

00:35:19.380 --> 00:35:20.580 line:80%
Finding Fan

00:35:21.460 --> 00:35:22.900 line:80%
won't be easy.

00:35:23.900 --> 00:35:25.500 line:80%
Outer disciples guard the town gate.

00:35:26.060 --> 00:35:27.460 line:80%
Xingjia should still be in town.

00:35:28.100 --> 00:35:29.300 line:80%
The inn is full of people,

00:35:29.613 --> 00:35:31.082 line:80%
not a suitable place to hide someone.

00:35:31.460 --> 00:35:32.300 line:80%
I think

00:35:33.020 --> 00:35:34.860 line:80%
he's hiding in a civilian house.

00:35:35.820 --> 00:35:37.122 line:80%
There must be at least 100 houses

00:35:37.133 --> 00:35:38.140 line:80%
in Qingque Town.

00:35:38.940 --> 00:35:41.140 line:80%
If we search recklessly,
it'll alert the enemy.

00:35:49.780 --> 00:35:50.620 line:80%
I have a plan.

00:35:55.100 --> 00:35:55.940 line:80%
Coming.

00:35:58.260 --> 00:35:59.620 line:80%
Miss, what's the matter?

00:36:00.100 --> 00:36:01.220 line:80%
I'm Cuihua, new here.

00:36:02.340 --> 00:36:04.460 line:80%
Last night, my mother
gave birth to a sister.

00:36:05.060 --> 00:36:07.060 line:80%
My father said I should deliver
celebratory eggs.

00:36:09.740 --> 00:36:11.620 line:80%
Miss, in Qingque Town,

00:36:11.700 --> 00:36:13.586 line:80%
celebratory eggs must be given
in even numbers.

00:36:14.660 --> 00:36:15.820 line:80%
I just moved here.

00:36:15.891 --> 00:36:16.880 line:80%
I didn't know the custom.

00:36:17.060 --> 00:36:17.940 line:80%
Here's another one.

00:36:18.540 --> 00:36:19.380 line:80%
Thank you.

00:36:20.460 --> 00:36:21.500 line:80%
Take care, miss.

00:36:25.370 --> 00:36:26.220 line:80%
Who is it?

00:36:26.260 --> 00:36:27.653 line:80%
I came to deliver celebratory eggs.

00:36:28.980 --> 00:36:30.260 line:80%
My mother gave birth to a sister.

00:36:30.340 --> 00:36:32.180 line:80%
Father said to deliver eggs.

00:36:32.270 --> 00:36:33.299 line:80%
Good things come in pairs.

00:36:34.300 --> 00:36:36.500 line:80%
- Who is it?
- I came to deliver eggs.

00:36:39.380 --> 00:36:40.220 line:80%
Thank you.

00:36:50.360 --> 00:36:51.419 line:80%
He doesn't know the custom.

00:36:51.660 --> 00:36:52.500 line:80%
He must be new here.

00:36:52.660 --> 00:36:54.340 line:80%
He has sharp eyes
and long-lasting energy.

00:36:54.900 --> 00:36:55.740 line:80%
He must be a master.

00:37:25.420 --> 00:37:26.260 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:37:32.733 --> 00:37:34.740 line:80%
(Qian Xueshen)
Are you trying to tire me to death?

00:37:34.740 --> 00:37:36.500 line:80%
Even a mule needs a break.

00:37:36.700 --> 00:37:37.960 line:80%
These past 15 days have drained

00:37:37.971 --> 00:37:38.751 line:80%
all my power.

00:37:38.886 --> 00:37:39.975 line:80%
I just rested for two days,

00:37:39.986 --> 00:37:40.740 line:80%
and you came again.

00:37:40.980 --> 00:37:42.060 line:80%
Mr. Qian, don't worry.

00:37:42.460 --> 00:37:43.940 line:80%
We wouldn't want to exhaust you.

00:37:44.580 --> 00:37:46.153 line:80%
This time, it doesn't require precision.

00:37:46.380 --> 00:37:47.620 line:80%
Please, Mr. Qian,

00:37:47.940 --> 00:37:48.820 line:80%
do your job.

00:37:59.340 --> 00:38:00.980 line:80%
He looks delicate

00:38:01.540 --> 00:38:02.433 line:80%
and has fragile bones.

00:38:03.420 --> 00:38:04.780 line:80%
He doesn't seem to be an elite.

00:38:06.220 --> 00:38:07.546 line:80%
Why do you want to transform him?

00:38:07.900 --> 00:38:09.340 line:80%
This kid is cunning,

00:38:09.900 --> 00:38:11.460 line:80%
sneaking into the Disciples' Dorm

00:38:11.460 --> 00:38:12.500 line:80%
at night to check luggage.

00:38:12.799 --> 00:38:14.013 line:80%
If not replaced with our own...

00:38:14.860 --> 00:38:15.700 line:80%
Enough.

00:38:16.020 --> 00:38:16.860 line:80%
Mr. Qian,

00:38:17.060 --> 00:38:17.900 line:80%
get to work.

00:38:36.220 --> 00:38:37.060 line:80%
I'll transform you.

00:39:12.500 --> 00:39:13.580 line:80%
The Face Shift.

00:39:14.540 --> 00:39:15.580 line:80%
It reappears.

00:39:16.500 --> 00:39:17.340 line:80%
You know again?

00:39:18.180 --> 00:39:19.020 line:80%
Don't look at me.

00:39:19.100 --> 00:39:20.060 line:80%
It's not my business.

00:39:20.700 --> 00:39:22.380 line:80%
The Body Shift is indeed wondrous,

00:39:22.740 --> 00:39:23.620 line:80%
perfectly executed.

00:39:24.020 --> 00:39:25.020 line:80%
This person can be killed

00:39:25.700 --> 00:39:26.753 line:80%
to prevent future trouble.

00:39:33.260 --> 00:39:34.300 line:80%
Please, spare me!

00:39:37.100 --> 00:39:37.940 line:80%
He just fainted?

00:39:40.580 --> 00:39:41.460 line:80%
Such a waste.

00:39:42.260 --> 00:39:43.100 line:80%
I'll chop him up.

00:39:43.340 --> 00:39:44.340 line:80%
I'm awake!

00:39:45.260 --> 00:39:46.100 line:80%
I'm awake.

00:39:46.420 --> 00:39:47.260 line:80%
I'm awake.

00:39:48.300 --> 00:39:49.873 line:80%
What's your connection to Qianmian Sect?

00:39:50.060 --> 00:39:50.900 line:80%
Who are you?

00:39:51.260 --> 00:39:53.180 line:80%
I'm Qian Xueshen,

00:39:53.220 --> 00:39:55.140 line:80%
the last descendant of Qianmian Sect.

00:39:55.460 --> 00:39:56.340 line:80%
Please understand.

00:39:56.740 --> 00:39:57.940 line:80%
They forced me to do this.

00:39:58.140 --> 00:39:59.820 line:80%
I'm just a scholar,

00:40:00.020 --> 00:40:00.995 line:80%
with elders and children

00:40:01.006 --> 00:40:01.700 line:80%
to care about.

00:40:09.480 --> 00:40:20.140 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:40:38.900 --> 00:40:43.310 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:40:43.875 --> 00:40:48.490 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:40:48.830 --> 00:40:53.395 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:40:53.920 --> 00:40:58.220 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:41:01.165 --> 00:41:05.865 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:06.390 --> 00:41:10.680 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:41:11.340 --> 00:41:15.370 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:41:15.685 --> 00:41:20.810 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:41:21.385 --> 00:41:26.195 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:26.410 --> 00:41:30.580 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:41:31.305 --> 00:41:35.240 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:41:35.740 --> 00:41:41.015 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:42:03.745 --> 00:42:08.875 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:42:09.240 --> 00:42:13.610 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:42:13.875 --> 00:42:18.005 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:42:18.190 --> 00:42:23.765 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪